</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Barcodes / Code</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The barcode of the variation (GTIN etc.).<br>
→ Use the drop-down list on the right to specify which type of barcode is saved in the column.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item texts / Item text</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The description text of the variation.<br>
→ Use the drop-down list on the right to specify which language the description text is saved in.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item images / URL</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">A link to an online image of the product<br>
